\n*[[Surveillance industry]]<ref name=\"spinoff\"/>\n*[[X-ray]] \u2014 [[X-ray detector]],<ref name=\"Kuo365\"/> [[digital radiography]],<ref name=\"DigImSys\">{{cite book|title=Digital imaging systems for plain radiography|last1=Lan\u00e7a|first1=Lu\u00eds|last2=Silva|first2=Augusto|date=2013|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-1-4614-5066-5|location=New York|pages=14\u201317|chapter=Digital Radiography Detectors: A Technical Overview|doi=10.1007/978-1-4614-5067-2_2|hdl=10400.21/1932}}</ref> [[flat-panel detector]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Kump|first1=K|last2=Grantors|first2=P|last3=Pla|first3=F|last4=Gobert|first4=P|date=December 1998|title=Digital X-ray detector technology|journal=RBM-News|volume=20|issue=9|pages=221\u2013226|doi=10.1016/S0222-0776(99)80006-6}}</ref>\n*Other uses \u2014 [[Unmanned aerial vehicle|Drones]], [[robots]], [[Telephoto lens|telescopic lens]]<ref>{{cite news |title=CMOS Image Sensors Market 2020 to 2025 By Technology Growth and Demand: STMicroelectronics N.V, Sony Corporation, Samsung Electronics |url=https://www.marketwatch.com/press-release/cmos-image-sensors-market-2020-to-2025-by-technology-growth-and-demand-stmicroelectronics-nv-sony-corporation-samsung-electronics-2020-03-09 |accessdate=17 April 2020 |work=[[MarketWatch]] |date=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Electronic components}}\n{{Logic Families}}\n{{Sensors}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:MOSFET applications}}\n[[Category:MOSFETs|Applications]]\n[[Category:1960 introductions]]\n[[Category:20th-century inventions]]\n[[Category:Arab inventions]]\n[[Category:Biosensors]]\n[[Category:Digital electronics]]\n[[Category:Electronic design]]\n[[Category:Integrated circuits]]\n[[Category:Semiconductor devices]]\n[[Category:Sensors]]\n[[Category:Silicon]]\n[[Category:Solid state switches]]\n[[Category:South Korean inventions]]\n[[Category:Transistor amplifiers]]\n[[Category:Transistor types]]\n[[Category:Transistors]]\n", "name_user": "Maestro2016", "label": "safe", "comment"