saan Samman Nidhi|publisher=[[CNBC TV18]]|accessdate=1 February 2019|url=https://www.cnbctv18.com/economy/union-budget-2019-2020-finance-minister-piyush-goyal-to-present-modi-governments-last-budget-today-focus-on-farm-loan-waiver-income-tax-slabs-2140711.htm}}</ref><ref name=\"12 Crore farmers to get benefit\">{{cite news|title=12 Crore farmers to get benefit|publisher=[[NewsX]]|accessdate=1 February 2019|url=https://www.newsx.com/national/7th-pay-commission-interim-budget-2019-piyush-goyal-live-updates-will-narendra-modi-government-make-any-announcement-on-salary-hike}}</ref><ref name=\"Interim Budget\">{{cite news|title=Interim Budget|publisher=[[Outlook India]]|accessdate=1 February 2019|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/website/story/business-news-budget-2019-live-litmus-test-for-modi-govt-as-piyush-goyal-is-set-to-present-interim-budget-today/324674}}</ref><ref name=\"Interim Budget 2019\">{{cite news|title=Interim Budget 2019|publisher=[[Zee News]]|accessdate=1 February 2019|url=https://zeenews.india.com/business/live-updates/interim-budget-2019-live-updates-2176100}}</ref> The scheme will cost {{INRConvert|75000|c|year=2019}} per annum and will come in effect from December 2018.<ref name=\"Goyal announces\">{{cite news|title=Goyal announces|publisher=dailyexcelsior.com|accessdate=1 February 2019|url=http://www.dailyexcelsior.com/goyal-announces-a-mega-pension-yojana-hikes-gratuity-limit-sobs-for-farmer/}}</ref> {{INR}}6,000 per year will be paid to each eligible farmer in three instalments and will be deposited directly to their bank accounts.<ref name=\"Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi scheme Approved\">{{cite news|title=Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi scheme Approved|publisher=dailyhunt.in|accessdate=1 February 2019|url=https://m.dailyhunt.in/news/india/english/east+coast+daily+eng-epaper-eeastco/interim+budget+2019+pradhan+mantri+kisan+samman+nidhi+scheme+approved-newsid-107689105}}</ref>\n\n==History==\nThe scheme was first conceived and implemented by [[Government of Telangana|Govt of Telangana]] as the [[Rythu Bandhu scheme|Rythu Bandhu]] scheme, where a certain amount is given directly to eligible farmers. The scheme has received accolades<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/world-bank-pat-for-rythu-bandhu-implementation/article26413088.ece|title=World Bank pat for Rythu Bandhu implementation|last=Rajeev|first=M.|date=2019-03-02|work=The Hindu|access-date=2019-04-03|language=en-IN|issn=0971-751X}}</ref> from various organisations for its successful implementation, including [[World Bank]]. Many economist suggest that this type of investment support is better<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.livemint.com/Politics/2719Mq7Dqo8c5xJ6s9xnJP/Telangana-shows-an-alternative-to-farm-loan-waivers.html|title=Telangana shows an alternative to farm loan waivers|last=Lasania|first=Yunus Y.|date=2018-12-26|website=Mint|language=en|access-date=2019-04-03}}</ref> than farm loan waivers. With the positive outcome of this scheme, [[Government of India|Govt of India]] wanted to implement<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/centre-replicates-telanganas-rythu-bandhu-scheme-give-income-support-farmers-96057|website=www.thenewsminute.com|access-date=2019-04-03|title=Centre replicates Telangana's Rythu Bandhu scheme to give income support to farmers|date=February 2019}}</ref> it as nationwide project and it was announced by [[Piyush Goyal]] during the [[2019 Interim Union Budget of India]] on 1 February 2019.<ref name=\"Interim Budget 20192\">{{cite news|url=https://zeenews.india.com/business/live-updates/interim-budget-2019-live-updates-2176100|title=Interim Budget 2019|accessdate=1 February 2019|publisher=[[Zee News]]}}</ref><ref name=\"Interim Budget2\">{{cite news|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/website/story/business-news-budget-2019-live-litmus-test-for-modi-govt-as-piyush-goyal-is-set-to-present-interim-budget-today/324674|title=Interim Budget|accessdate=1 February 2019|publisher=[[Outlook India]]}}</ref>\n\nOn 24 February 2019, [[Narendra Modi]] launched the scheme in [[Uttar Pradesh]]'s [[Gorakhpur]] by transferring the first instalment of \u20b92,000 each to over one crore farmers.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/pm-launches-kisan-scheme-over-1-crore-farmers-get-1st-instalment/article26356409.ece|title=Modi launches PM-Kisan scheme from Gorakhpur|last=Bureau|first=Our|website=@businessline|language=en|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatvnews.com/video/politics/pm-modi-launches-pradhan-mantri-kisan-samman-nidhi-yojana-other-initiatives-in-gorakhpur-506022|title=VIDEO: PM Modi launches Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi Yojana, other initiatives in Gorakhpur|website=www.indiatvnews.com|language=en|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ani/pm-modi-unveils-pradhan-mantri-kisan-samman-nidhi-scheme-in-gorakhpur-119022400232_1.html|title=PM Modi unveils Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi scheme in Gorakhpur|last=ANI|date=2019-02-24|work=Business Standard India|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref> \u00a0\n\n== Objectives ==\n\n# With a view to augment the income of the Small and Marginal Farmers (SMFs), the Government has launched a new Central Sector Scheme, namely, \"Pradhan Mantri KIsan SAmman Nidhi (PM-KISAN)\" in the current financial year.<ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=http://pmkisan.nic.in/Documents/PMKisanSamanNidhi.PDF|title=Objectives of PM-Kisan|website=pmkisan.nic.in}}</ref>\n# The PM-KISAN scheme aims to supplement the financial needs of the SMFs in procuring various inputs to ensure proper crop health and appropriate yields, commensurate with the anticipated farm income at the end of the each crop cycle.<ref name=\":1\" />\n# This would also protect them from falling in the clutches of moneylenders for meeting such expenses and ensure their continuance in the farming activities.<ref name=\":1\" />\n\n==Finance==\nThis is error {{INR}}75,000 crore.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=187932|title=Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi announced to provide assured income support to small and marginal farmers|website=pib.nic.in|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref> The complete expenditure for the scheme will borne by the Union Government in 2019-20.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pmkisan.nic.in/|title=pmkisan.nic.in|website=pmkisan.nic.in}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jagranjosh.com/current-affairs/states-urged-for-speedy-implementation-of-pradhan-mantri-kisan-samman-nidhi-yojana-pm-kisan-portal-launched-1549604418-1|title=Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi Yojana: Guidelines launched for States to implement scheme; PM-Kisan Portal launched|date=2019-02-08|website=Jagranjosh.com|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/centre-seeks-to-emulate-telangana-and-odisha-through-annual-rs-6000-each-to-over-12-crore-farmers/articleshow/67796488.cms|title=Farm de-stress yojana to benefit 12 crore - Times of India|website=The Times of India|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref>\n\n==Eligibility criteria==\n\n# In the database, the land owner's name, gender.\n# Social Classification (Scheduled Tribes / Scheduled Tribes).\n# [[Aadhaar]] number, bank account number and mobile number etc.\n# Land record details.\n# Jan Dhan Bank Account Number, Aadhaar and Mobile Number will help in identifying eligible beneficiaries and incompetent claimants.\n#The scheme is sponsored by the Central Government. Therefore, the farmers have to be citizens of the country.\n\n=== Documents required ===\n\n# Citizenship certificate <ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiafilings.com/learn/pradhan-mantri-kisan-samman-nidhi-yojana/|title=Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi Yojana - IndiaFilings|date=2019-02-13|website=IndiaFilings - Learning Centre|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref>\n# Landholding papers <ref name=\":0\" />\n# Aadhaar card <ref name=\":0\" />\n# Bank account details <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/faqs/miscellaneous/pradhan-mantri-kisan-samman-nidhi-check-eligibility-dates-and-other-details-here/articleshow/68049751.cms|title=Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi: Check eligibility, dates and other details here - Times of India|website=The Times of India|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref>\n\n=== Exclusion categories ===\nThe following categories of beneficiaries of higher economic status shall not be eligible for benefit under the scheme.<ref name=\":2\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pmkisan.nic.in|title=Exclusion categories|website=pmkisan.nic.in}}</ref><ref name=\":3\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.financialexpress.com/economy/pm-kisan-samman-nidhi-govt-announces-exclusion-criteria-check-who-wont-get-it/1479544/|title=PM Kisan scheme: Govt announces exclusion criteria \u2013 Check who won't get it|date=2019-02-07|website=The Financial Express|access-date=2019-02-24}}</ref>\n\n(A) All Institutional Land holders.<ref name=\":2\" /><ref name=\":3\" />\n\n(B) Farmer families in which one or more of its members belong to following categories:<ref name=\":2\" /><ref name=\":3\" />\n\n# Former and present holders of constitutional posts.\n# Former and present Ministers/ State Ministers and former/present Members of [[Lok Sabha|LokSabha]]/ [[Rajya Sabha|RajyaSabha]]/ State Legislative Assemblies/ State Legislative Councils,former and present Mayors of Municipal Corporations, former and present Chairpersons of District Panchayats.\n# All serving or retired officers and employees of Central/ State Government Ministries /Offices/Departments and its field units Central or State PSEs and Attached offices /Autonomous Institutions under Government as well as regular employees of the Local Bodies (Excluding Multi Tasking Staff /Class IV/Group D employees).\n# All superannuated/retired pensioners whose monthly pension is {{INR}}10,000/-or more (Excluding Multi Tasking Staff / Class IV/Group D employees) of above category.\n# All Persons who paid Income Tax in last assessment year.\n# Professionals like Doctors, Engineers, Lawyers, Chartered Accountants, and Architects registered with Professional bodies and carrying out profession by undertaking practices.\n\n== State Governments Schemes ==\n\n===Annadatha Sukhibhava===\n{{Infobox project\n| name       = Annadatha Sukhibhava\n| budget = \u20b95,000 crores for FY 2019-20\n| location       = [[Andhra Pradesh]], [[India]]\n| website      = http://annadathasukhibhava.ap.gov.in/\n}}\n'''Annadatha Sukhibhava''' ({{lang-te|\u0c05\u0c28\u0c4d\u0c28\u0c26\u0c3e\u0c24 \u0c38\u0c41\u0c16\u0c40\u0c2d\u0c35}}) is a welfare program started by [[Government of Andhra Pradesh|Andhra Pradesh Government]] to provide \u20b915,000 investment support to small and marginal farmer's family per annum which includes \u20b96000 Central Government Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi share.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/india/andhra-to-give-all-farmers-rs-10000-merges-pm-kisan-scheme-with-annadatha-sukhibhava-5582088/|title=Andhra merges PM Kisan scheme with Annadatha Sukhibhava, all farmers to get Rs 10,000|date=2019-02-14|website=The Indian Express|language=en-IN|access-date=2019-04-13}}</ref> The government is providing support to nearly 64.1 lakh farmer including [[tenant farmer]]s.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aninews.in/news/national/general-news/54-lakh-andhra-farmers-to-get-benefit-of-annadata-sukhibhava-scheme-2019-somireddy-chandramohan-reddy20190216230913/|title=54 lakh Andhra farmers to get benefit of Annadata Sukhibhava scheme 2019: Somireddy Chandramohan Reddy|website=www.aninews.in|language=en|access-date=2019-04-13}}</ref> This farmer investment support scheme where the cash is paid directly into the [[Aadhaar]] linked bank accounts will cover all the farmers in the state on Family as unit basis without any conditions.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/5000-cr-allocated-for-annadata-sukhibhava/article26187674.ece|title=\u20b95,000 cr. allocated for \u2018Annadata Sukhibhava\u2019|last=Rao|first=G. Venkataramana|date=2019-02-06|work=The Hindu|access-date=2019-04-13|language=en-IN|issn=0971-751X}}</ref> It was formally started on 19-02-2019 by providing \u20b91000 Initially by [[Real Time Governance Society|Real Time Governance Society center]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://newindianexpress.com/cities/vijayawada/2019/feb/19/annadata-sukhibhava-launched--nearly-50l-get-rs-1000-on-day-one-1940790.html|title=Annadata Sukhibhava launched, nearly 50 lakh get Rs 1,000 on Day One|website=The New Indian Express|access-date=2019-02-21}}</ref>\n\n====Payment disbursal====\n[[Government of Andhra Pradesh|Andhra Pradesh Government]] was displaying the number of families benefiting with this scheme in real time basis on its official website.\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+'''Annadatha Sukhibhava Payment Dashboard''' <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://annadathasukhibhava.ap.gov.in/ADSBAPP/kisan/index|title=:: Annadatha Sukhibhava ::|website=annadathasukhibhava.ap.gov.in|access-date=2019-04-10}}</ref>'''( As on 13-04-2019; 12 PM )'''\n!Term\n!Amount\n!Date of Initiation\n!'''Families Eligible'''\n!'''Payment Initiated'''\n!'''Payment Success'''\n!'''Under Process'''\n!Amount\n|-\n|Phase 1\n|\u20b9 1000\n|17-02-2019\n|50,19,383\n|50,16,443\n|46,21,658\n|3,97,725\n|\u20b9 462.17 Cr\n|-\n|Phase 2\n|\u20b9 3000\n|03-04-2019\n|48,92,682\n|45,03,431\n|44,43,721\n|4,48,961\n|\u20b9 1333.12 Cr\n|-\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n\n== Amratvih ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+\n!Aspect\n!PM-Kisan\n![[Rythu Bandhu scheme|Rythu Bandhu]]\n![[Annadatha Sukhibhava]]\n!KALIA scheme<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/states/odisha/2019/jan/05/what-is-kalia-scheme-and-who-is-eligible-to-get-benefit-1921003.html|title=What is Kalia scheme and who is eligible to get its benefits?|website=The New Indian Express|access-